Package: MSfmtR
Title: MSfmtR: An R package for formatting mass spectrometry data
Version: 0.6-3
Authors@R: person("Randy", "Johnson", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "randall.johnson@nih.gov")
Description: MSfmtR is an R package for formatting mass spectrometry data. It includes functions for filtering, importing files into MSstats, and creating output suitable for use in the ProtResDash package. The package is designed to be flexible and extensible, allowing users to easily add new file formats and data processing methods.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
